      <h2>
        <span class="en">Explicit degradation over hidden recovery</span>
        <span class="es">Degradación explícita antes que recuperación oculta</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="creed reveal">
      <div class="rule"><span class="mark">01</span><span><span class="en">If consensus cannot be established, the system <strong>preserves uncertainty</strong>.</span><span class="es">Si el consenso no puede establecerse, el sistema <strong>preserva la incertidumbre</strong>.</span></span></div>
      <div class="rule"><span class="mark">02</span><span><span class="en">If migration cannot be completed, the memory <strong>remains in place</strong>.</span><span class="es">Si la migración no puede completarse, el recuerdo <strong>permanece donde está</strong>.</span></span></div>
      <div class="rule"><span class="mark">03</span><span><span class="en">If the audit cannot be written, the state transition <strong>is rejected</strong>.</span><span class="es">Si la auditoría no puede escribirse, la transición de estado <strong>se rechaza</strong>.</span></span></div>
      <p class="final">
        <span class="en">The system never fabricates certainty in order to preserve availability.</span>
